if the conditions were fulfilled, be paid? The advertisement says that £1000
is lodged at the bank for the purpose. Therefore, it cannot be said that the
statement that £100 would be paid was intended to be a mere puff." His
Lordship also exposed the fallacy of the argument that an offer could not
be made to the world at large, when he said: "Why should not an offer be
