special pass of admission to a film studio which showed his photograph
and the official stamp. This convinced the plaintiff and he allowed the car
to be taken away for the cheque. The rogue lost no time in disposing of
the car to an innocent buyer, the defendant. The worthless cheque came
back and the plaintiff sued the defendant to recover his car.
