competing or liable to compete in any way with the business for the time
being carried on by the company. He afterwards entered into agreement
with another manufacturer of guns and ammunition and the company
brought an action to restrain him.
It was held that first part of the agreement was valid being reasonably
necessary for the protection of the purchaser's interest. But the rest of the
covenant by which he was prohibited from competing with the company
